      <description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;b&gt;1st year&lt;/b&gt; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Lesson of the Devoted&lt;/u&gt;: The player is surrounded by a beautiful blue/white glow as they gain double experience for half an hour every 20 hours.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;2nd year&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Infusion of the Faithful&lt;/u&gt;: Usable once every 20 hours, the player enjoys maximum resistances and statistics and a faster run speed for 15 minutes while he glows brightly with power.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;3rd year&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Chaotic Jester&lt;/u&gt;: Summons a Bristlebane puppet that persists for 15 minutes. Usable once every 20 hours, Bristlebane will randomly cast various spells that provide benefits or minor penalties.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;4th year&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;br&gt;Expedient Recovery&lt;/u&gt;: Usable once per week, all the player’s corpses are summoned to their feet and given 100% experience resurrection.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;5th year&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Steadfast Servant&lt;/u&gt;: Summons a creature that casts healing spells upon the player and others nearby. Lasts for half an hour and is usable once every 20 hours.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;6th year&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Staunch Recovery&lt;/u&gt;: Usable once every 3 days, the player is fully healed with health, mana, and endurance fully restored.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;7th year&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Intensity of the Resolute&lt;/u&gt;: Increases the power of the player’s abilities and heals substantially for 5 minutes once every 20 hours while the player is surrounded by a glow of energy.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;8th year&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;Throne of Heroes&lt;/u&gt;: Usable every 72 minutes, the player is teleported to the Throne of Heroes in the Guild Lobby.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Kytherea on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;06-29-2006&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;10:43 AM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
